 told|url=http://www.thehindu.com/2004/03/04/stories/2004030402050500.htm|website=The Hindu|accessdate=March 4, 2004}}</ref> (2004, Yabaluri) # Living Through Changing Times (2007, Yabaluri) # Vidya Rangamulo Samasyalu (Telugu) (Telugu Vidyardhi)
