ree Ramayana Mahanveshanam A Set Of Two Volumes|origyear=2010|year= 2010|publisher=Roopa Publications, New Delhi|isbn=}} *{{cite book |last=Narasimhacharya|first= R|title= History of Kannada Literature |origyear=1988|year=1988|publisher=Asian Educational Services|location= New Delhi|isbn= 81-206-0303-6 }} *{{cite book |last=Nagaraj |first=D.R.|editor=Sheldon I. Pollock|title=Literary Cultures in History: Reconstructions from South Asia |year=2003|location=Berkeley and London |publisher=University of California Press |chapter=Critical Tensions in the History of Kannada Literary Culture|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xowUxYhv0QgC&pg=PA323&dq=critical+tensions+in+history+kannada+literary+culture|isbn=0-520-22821-9 |pages=323&ndash;383}} *{{cite book |last= Prashad|first= K Kehsavan|title=Male Madeshwara: A Kannada Oral Epic|origyear=2001|year=2001|location=New Delhi|publisher=Sahitya Akademi|isbn=81-260-0925-X}} *{{cite book |last=Parmeshwaranand|first=Swami|title=Encyclopaedic Dictionary of Puranas, Volume 3 (I-L)|origyear=2001|year=2001|publisher=Sarup and Sons, New Delhi|isbn=81-7625-226-3}} *{{cite book |last=Parmeshwaranand|first=Swami|title=Encyclopaedic Dictionary of Puranas, Volume 4 (M-R)|origyear=2001|year=2001|publisher=Sarup and Sons, New Delhi|isbn=81-7625-226-3}} *{{cite book |last = Pollock | first = Sheldon | authorlink = Sheldon Pollock | title = The Language of Gods in the World of Men: Sanskrit, Culture and Power in Pre-modern India | year = 2006 | publisher = Berkeley and London: University of California Press. Pp. 703 | isbn = 0-520-24500-8 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=0UCh7r2TjQIC&dq}} *{{cite book |last= |first=|editor=Paula Richman|title= Ramayana Stories in Modern South India: An Anthology|origyear=2008|year=2008|publisher=Indiana University Press, Bloomington |isbn=978-0-253-21953-4}} *{{cite book |last= Puranik|first=Siddya|editor=Mohan Lal|title= Encyclopaedia of Indian literature&nbsp;– vol 5|origyear=1992|year=1